---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout active="developers" title="Adamant — Faucet" description="Testnet faucet. Rate-limited test ADM for development.">
  <section class="page-intro">
    <div class="container">
      <div>
        <div class="crumb">§ Developers · /developers/faucet</div>
        <h1 class="title">Testnet faucet.</h1>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="lede">Test ADM, capped per address per day. For local development and CI. Production load belongs on burn-to-mint, not the faucet.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="border: 1px solid var(--ink); padding: 28px;">
        <span class="label">Request · pre-launch</span>
        <div style="display:flex; gap: 0; border: 1px solid var(--rule-2); margin-top: 12px;">
          <input class="mono" placeholder="adm1… (testnet address)" style="flex:1; border: 0; padding: 14px 16px; font-size: 13px; background: var(--paper); color: var(--ink-2); outline: none; min-width: 0;"/>
          <button class="mono" disabled style="border: 0; border-left: 1px solid var(--rule-2); background: var(--ink-3); color: var(--paper); padding: 14px 18px; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; cursor: not-allowed;">Drip (offline)</button>
        </div>
        <p class="mono small" style="color: var(--ink-3); margin-top: 14px;">Faucet activates at public testnet. Rate limit will be 100 testnet ADM per address per 24h.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="callout" style="margin-top: 28px;">
        <div class="mark-c">§</div>
        <div>
          <p>Testnet ADM is not transferable to mainnet. Burn-to-mint is the only path for real ADM. The faucet is an integration tool, not a launch mechanism.</p>
          <small>— Faucet policy</small>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
